body.description: SmartyPants Organics Toddler Complete is a certified-organic and certified-vegetarian multifunctional dietary supplement formulated just for the little guys (and gals). We know you're always striving to keep your toddler healthy and happy. We are too. That's why we use the most premium organic ingredients and pack them into one easy-to-take gummy that even picky toddlers love. Each serving delivers vegetarian omega-3, probiotics, and 14 essential nutrients, including vitamin D as D3 to support bone health, B12 vitamins to support energy metabolism ,and zinc to support healthy immune function all in one delicious gummy. They are also an excellent source of vitamins A, C, D, E, B6, B12, folate, biotin, and iodine.
